00:09:03,008 --> 00:09:04,888
This is like pre-Apex Legends kind of numbers.

230
00:09:05,529 --> 00:09:07,789
At 1.5 million signups, we're on top of the world, right?

231
00:09:07,829 --> 00:09:09,890
Like our random garage game had just suddenly

232
00:09:09,930 --> 00:09:10,270
like hit a.

