00:31:05,381 --> 00:31:08,742
and I click go again and I get a completely different one, and go again and I get a different.

826
00:31:08,782 --> 00:31:11,464
So, by default here, it's producing random levels.

827
00:31:11,544 --> 00:31:15,906
Now, these are relatively similar, because it's just a relatively simple one, but I'll make it more complicated.

828
00:31:16,226 --> 00:31:19,988
So, I can then play this in-game, and sure enough, there's a pretty bridge over the river,

829
00:31:20,048 --> 00:31:23,270
and it works out the direction of the water flow, and does all the fancy foam generation.

830
00:31:23,290 --> 00:31:26,291
All this cool stuff just happens, because we've got mature tools for that now.

831
00:31:27,715 --> 00:31:29,296
And so I say, okay, so this is a forest.

832
00:31:29,316 --> 00:31:30,397
I need some stuff to fill it with.

