00:31:36,260 --> 00:31:37,381
And it puts them throughout the level.

837
00:31:37,841 --> 00:31:39,722
And then I generate again and get a different set of stuff

838
00:31:39,902 --> 00:31:40,962
and again and get a different one.

839
00:31:41,163 --> 00:31:43,184
And the player story is subtly different each time.

