00:31:47,366 --> 00:31:48,867
And you have to bear in mind that this was like

844
00:31:49,367 --> 00:31:51,188
literally just a cross in the editor,

845
00:31:51,208 --> 00:31:53,369
like the simplest possible graph that took seconds to do.

