00:31:56,791 --> 00:31:59,092
This is the river crossing that's to the left of Act 2 town.

848
00:31:59,432 --> 00:32:03,034
And the way that this all works is instead of doing levels like this,

849
00:32:03,175 --> 00:32:04,895
where you just make one and hope it's random enough,

850
00:32:05,136 --> 00:32:06,877
you make like 20 different variations.

851
00:32:06,897 --> 00:32:09,438
You have two rivers, you have five rivers, you have no rivers.

852
00:32:09,758 --> 00:32:12,420
You have it so that there's multiple roads or a fork in the road.

853
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:13,520
You have all of these crazy things.

