00:32:13,820 --> 00:32:15,541
And then when the game is generating the level,

855
00:32:15,802 --> 00:32:17,522
it picks which topology to use first,

856
00:32:17,582 --> 00:32:19,424
and then it does the random generation within it.

857
00:32:19,684 --> 00:32:21,225
And so you've got two levels of randomness there.

