00:34:00,379 --> 00:34:01,080
Now to give an example,

903
00:34:01,140 --> 00:34:02,481
imagine you're a Path of Exile designer,

904
00:34:02,501 --> 00:34:04,222
your job is to make encounters like fights.

905
00:34:04,262 --> 00:34:05,924
So you're sitting at your desk and I come over and say,

