00:34:43,904 --> 00:34:45,305
Randomly, some of these are going to be bosses.

926
00:34:45,325 --> 00:34:48,486
So sure enough, the fight's no different because you get lucky or unlucky with how many bosses there are.

927
00:34:49,006 --> 00:34:51,687
Then we're going to add some random mods to the fight, and so on and so on.

928
00:34:51,707 --> 00:34:55,549
So each axis increases it, and it gets to the point where you've done five times the work,

929
00:34:55,609 --> 00:34:59,330
but got ten thousand times the amount of randomness out, versus just making 50 encounters,

930
00:34:59,390 --> 00:35:02,552
and then it gets boring once they've played all 50, which is the prophecy league.

