00:45:27,540 --> 00:45:29,320
which is going to have a place in the world one day,

1190
00:45:29,340 --> 00:45:30,761
and we just pick some things for the league.

1191
00:45:31,281 --> 00:45:32,321
And I'll give you another example.

1192
00:45:32,781 --> 00:45:34,022
