1214
00:46:05,491 --> 00:46:06,752
for this current league, potentially.

1215
00:46:07,012 --> 00:46:09,453
And it's just so good to have that giant library of stuff.

1216
00:46:10,953 --> 00:46:11,934
Okay, so in conclusion.

1217
00:46:12,772 --> 00:46:14,475
We initially released Path of Exile,

1218
00:46:14,515 --> 00:46:15,757
kind of failed at getting any growth,

1219
00:46:15,817 --> 00:46:16,798
then we turned things around

1220
00:46:16,839 --> 00:46:18,421
with this aggressive 13 week schedule,

1221
00:46:18,761 --> 00:46:20,544
