1235
00:47:01,314 --> 00:47:04,055
and supporter packs because they're available for when they next want to play.

1236
00:47:04,316 --> 00:47:06,317
And this is amazing because this is actually what we care about,

1237
00:47:06,337 --> 00:47:07,777
is keeping the community engaged.

1238
00:47:08,017 --> 00:47:10,799
And that community is never going below 50% during the quiet periods.

1239
00:47:11,339 --> 00:47:15,963
What's also interesting is the size of the community right at the end there, in terms of people accessing the website,

1240
00:47:16,203 --> 00:47:19,065
is a perfect predictor for server numbers for the next league.

1241
00:47:19,325 --> 00:47:23,568
So far, for like, you know, three years in a row, we've been able to predict server capacity for each launch

1242
00:47:23,849 --> 00:47:28,172
because of just looking at the website activity and using some ratios, and that's worked really well.

1243
00:47:28,933 --> 00:47:32,395
So anyway, the vindication we have with this whole plan is the fact that...

1244
00:47:33,907 --> 00:47:39,630
The fact that year after year we've managed to both grow our player numbers, but also get to the point where people never really leave Path of Exile.

1245
00:47:39,770 --> 00:47:42,711
They're still playing it, even if they say, I'm done with this league, I'll see you guys in a few months.

1246
00:47:42,751 --> 00:47:46,293
We know they're coming back, and they reliably do, they reliably keep spending and having a good time.

1247
00:47:46,573 --> 00:47:49,034
And this is the motivation we need to keep releasing quality content.

1248
00:47:50,233 --> 00:47:52,354
