00:51:38,175 --> 00:51:39,336
even without the additional traffic.

1336
00:51:39,376 --> 00:51:40,617
We can tell who the new users are.

1337
00:51:40,637 --> 00:51:41,458
It was certainly helpful.

1338
00:51:41,958 --> 00:51:45,221
But yeah, it is useful when fortuitous events happen.

